wiki.text:
'Primal' can refer to:
* An old term for a hypersurface in mathematics.
* Primal (verb or noun) denotes the reliving of an early painful feeling
  according to the primal therapy of Arthur Janov
* ''Primal'', a season 1 episode of Eureka
* ''Primal'', an action video game for the PlayStation 2
* Primal Pictures, the producer of 3D Interactive Anatomy Software,
  established in 1991
* Optimus Primal
* Several types of cuts of beef, primarily classified as either American
  Primals, or British Primals.
* ''Primal'', the Australian DVD title of the 2010 film The Lost Tribe
* Primal, 2010 horror film by Josh Reed with Zoe Tuckwell-Smith, Krew Boylan and
  Lindsay Farris
